rit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">muscles used</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;makes rowing a huge calorie burner. With rowing, you can achieve superb aerobic fitness and core strength. You will tone your upper and lower body while promoting great joint health through the wide range of motion rowing requires. If you have only a few minutes a day to exercise, the whole body nature of rowing will provide an efficient, effective workout that other exercises simply can&rsquo;t.</span></p>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 24px; font-family: ProximaNovaRegular; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">A Sport for All</span></h2>\n\n<p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; font-family: ProximaNovaRegular; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(97, 97, 97); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.concept2.com/indoor-rowers/testimonials\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 106, 177); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">People turn to rowing for many reasons</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: training for a world championship, recovery from injury, cardiac rehabilitation, managing diabetes, keeping fit for their primary sport, losing weight, camaraderie&hellip;the list goes on. And we hear from people every week who&rsquo;ve not only achieved their goals with rowing, they&rsquo;ve far surpassed them. Rowing works for kids, 100-year-olds, and everyone in between. It works for&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.concept2.com/indoor-rowers/adaptive-rowing\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 106, 177); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">adaptive athletes</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, elite athletes, and people who&rsquo;ve never been athletic before. Whatever your goals or experience, rowing will work for you, too.</span></p>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 24px; font-family: ProximaNovaRegular; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Machines that are Built to Last</span></h2>\n\n<p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; font-family: ProximaNovaRegular; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(97, 97, 97); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We&rsquo;ve been making indoor rowers since 1981. While other indoor rowers have come and gone, ours have become the best-selling indoor rowing machines in the world. We build our machines to last a lifetime, we price them fairly, and we stand behind our products. When you choose Concept2, you invest in a 40 year legacy of excellence. You reap the benefits of our passion and our drive to produce the highest quality products at the lowest possible price.</sp