INSERT INTO `wl_testimonial` VALUES (23,'','Wendy G','wendy-g-23','wendy@diamondFitnessgym.com','As a gym owner who has bought and sold through AME Fitness equipment, I can say that every experience has been a good one. They are reliable and courteous, we have reached a fair and successful deal every time. When they purchased equipment, they paid up front and when they delivered, picked up or moved equipment for us, the work was timely and professional. I highly recommend them for anyone in need of these services & products.',NULL,'2015-12-23 22:53:00','1'),(21,'0','Steve Body King','steve-body-king-21','thebodykingstudio@gmail.com','We went to Andy looking to upgrade a few treadmills and trade in a few strength pieces.  He showed us his showroom which was new and clean and had a great selection of both cardio and strength equipment.  He opened up the Life Fitness 97i treadmills to the motor and showed us how well kept they were.  No dust!   We bought 5.  Even when we asked about a T-Bar Row that he didn\'t have, he said he would try and find.  He called us a few weeks later and gave us a great deal on it.  6 months later we love all of the equipment that we upgraded to through Andy and we will definitely do business with AME Fitness Equipment again! Steve & Dwayne, The Body King Studio',NULL,'2015-11-30 20:22:26','1'),(22,'0','Sven Hida MD','sven-hida-md','sven@svendoctor.com','To whom it may concern,\n\nI have had the pleasure of meeting Andy Serrano, a knowledgeable businessman and owner of AME Custom Work Corp (DBA) AME Fitness Equipment while scouring the advertisements on Craig\'s list in search of a commercial-grade treadmill. Sifting through multiple postings and after having given Amazon and eBay a try, I ended up contacting Andy by chance with several inquiries regarding a treadmill I had my heart set on. I have had many years of experience in both buying and selling on Craig\'s list as well as eBay and developed an acute sense for knowing what someone is all about from their initial reply. I was pleasantly surprised by Andy\'s level of professionalism and courtesy, his polite demeanor and sense of trustworthiness knowing absolutely nothing about him nor his company. I had explained what I was looking for and was given several options as well as a detailed explanation of the work involved. I decided to forgo the less expensive \"clean and service\" option for the \"factory remanufactured\" option which I was told was a complete strip-down of the treadmill, replacement of most parts that undergo wear and tear and sanding and repainting of the treadmill. Andy promised photos of the process and delivered without needing to be reminded, photos and videos of what was involved and the progress of the job. I was presented with a professional invoice and multiple convenient payment options which as anyone knows, is not anywhere near standard for Craig\'s list. I had requested delivery and installation of the treadmill and not only was he and his crew on time as promised, but they were all very professional, had excellent comradery and rapport and worked together ensuring no damage would be done to my home and treadmill. I not only recommended his services and company to family, my closest friends and professional colleagues but continue to do so hands down without hesitation. I know that should I need any other work-out equipment, upholstery of gym equipment or furniture and delivery, he is my absolute first stop. It is rare to find an individual so dedicated and invested in his work, proud of his accomplishments and his excellence in service. In my experience with Andy Serrano, I found honesty, dedication and workmanship that is second to none.\n\nSincerely,\n\nSven Hida, MD',NULL,'2015-12-08 08:22:35','1'),(24,'0','Danielle Fields','danielle-fields','Danielle.fields@gmail.com','AME has a great selection of high-quality, late model commercial equipment for professional or home use.  They have all the best brands Cybex, Precor, Octane etc.  I purchased a commercial elliptical for a great price and they delivered and installed it in my home.  For the price of a high end model in one of the big-box sporting good stores, get yourself a like-new professional machine.',NULL,'2015-12-29 11:22:26','1'),(25,'0','Mike Abriano','mike-abriano','mabriano@yahoo.com','Picked up a used utility bench for my home gym.  Service was top notch - Andy went out of his way to ensure that customer satisfaction was achieved.  All the products he was selling appeared to be in good condition. Stand up guy. Would do business with again.',NULL,'2015-12-29 11:27:34','1'),(26,'0','Mario and Yami','mario-and-yami-26','250fitnessny@gmail.com','If you want to find good quality fitness equipment for the best value, we highly recommend to checkout AME Fitness equipment.  They have a huge selection of late model equipment for professional and home use.  If they dont have it there, they will find it for you.  Andy, the owner, helped us through the selection process.  We bought 6 different machines, varying from treadmills to a squat power rack.  He was very honest and professional on what would be best for us.  They give you step by step progress and visuals on the service they provide for your equipment, leaving them practically brand new.  The equipment was ready, delivered, and installed in our personal training facility in a timely manner.  With such great customer service and product to match, we will continue to do business with AME Fitness Equipment.',NULL,'2015-12-30 07:21:16','1'),(29,'0','Lindsey Greeley','lindsey-greeley','LindseyGreeley0912@gmail.com','I recently purchased a refurbished Stairmaster SM5 Stepmill, it looked brand new.!! I\'m a cardio queen especially when in competition season, so it\'s much more convenient to own your own Stairmaster but I simply could not afford a brand new one. With a very helpful staff I was very very pleased with my purchase from them and loving my Stepmill.',NULL,'2016-02-06 05:17:20','1'),(30,'0','Irene Poniros','irene-poniros','Irene.poniros@gmail.com','Pleasantly surprised with the fast service of my treadmill. It was a great experience dealing with Andy Serrano. Once my treadmill was delivered and set up for me I thought something was wrong and I called Andy and he literally came the next afternoon to fix the issue which was really something small. He showed me and fixed it in less than 10 minutes.  But wow talk about customer service and what a gentlemen.',NULL,'2016-02-06 05:34:55','1'),(31,'','Robert Hamill','robert-hamill-31','Rg_hamill@hotmail.com','I looked for a long time for power half racks and came across one of Andy\'s listings on eBay. His prices were very competitive and he had quality gear that was just hard to find anywhere let alone for the price he offered. As a bonus he is located Deer Park which is not hard to get to from CT. I purchased a great Hammer Strength half rack for my home gym and could not be happier.',NULL,'2016-03-08 08:04:01','0'),(32,'','Robert Hamill','robert-hamill-32','Rg_hamill@hotmail.com','I looked for a long time for power half racks and came across one of Andy\'s listings on eBay. His prices were very competitive and he had quality gear that was just hard to find anywhere let alone for the price he offered. As a bonus he is located Deer Park which is not hard to get to from CT. I purchased a great Hammer Strength half rack for my home gym and could not be happier.',NULL,'2016-03-08 08:04:29','0'),(33,'','Robert Hamill','robert-hamill-33','Rg_hamill@hotmail.com','I looked for a long time for power half racks and came across one of Andy\'s listings on eBay. His prices were very competitive and he had quality gear that was just hard to find anywhere let alone for the price he offered. As a bonus he is located Deer Park which is not hard to get to from CT. I purchased a great Hammer Strength half rack for my home gym and could not be happier.',NULL,'2016-03-08 08:05:00','0'),(34,'','Mark','mark-34','markrutledge1@gmail.com','I found AME Fitness Equipment through Ebay where I was looking for an MTS Ab Crunch Machine for me home. Andy was great to work with and very helpful in making sure I received my equipment. He went above and beyond to deliver and install the equipment in my apartment at a reasonable rate within my budget. The equipment is in great condition and works very well. AME Fitness Equipment and Andy are great to work with and provide reliable, top quality fitness equipment. I\'m so thankful I found them!',NULL,'2016-04-18 18:50:14','0'),(35,'','Meredith Spector','meredith-spector-35','mls@optonline.net','I purchased a pre-owned Cybex Arctrainer from someone I found on Craigslist and needed someone to transport it to my house.  Realizing that I needed more than my 17 year old son and his friends to disassemble and move the 500 pound machine, I found AME online and they handled the whole move for me . They were on time, professional and extremely pleasant to deal with.  All around great customer service experience! Thank you Andy and team - I will use you again!',NULL,'2016-05-20 21:49:57','0'),(36,'','Cassie Ferrara','cassie-ferrara-36','cassie.ferrara@yahoo.com','I have been looking for a spin bike for a long time and finally made the effort to do so. I searched fitness equipment stores and found AME Fitness Equipment. Andy was extremely helpful and knowledgable in helping me pick out the right spin bike!. I recently purchase the NXT Star Trac Spin Bike. I am loving my purchase from them. The bike was sold to me in outstanding condition and I have been spinning ever since I purchased it!.  Andy works VERY WELL with the customers and makes you feel comfortable about your purchase.  I HIGHLY reccommend this company, Andy is excellent.  Thank you for making my at home Spinning finally come to reality :)',NULL,'2016-05-26 07:58:57','0');
